1/* $NetBSD: therm.h,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:30 riastradh Exp $ */
2
3#ifndef __NVBIOS_THERM_H__
4#define __NVBIOS_THERM_H__
5struct nvbios_therm_threshold {
6 u8 temp;
7 u8 hysteresis;
8};
9
10struct nvbios_therm_sensor {
11 /* diode */
12 s16 slope_mult;
13 s16 slope_div;
14 s16 offset_num;
15 s16 offset_den;
16 s8 offset_constant;
17
18 /* thresholds */
19 struct nvbios_therm_threshold thrs_fan_boost;
20 struct nvbios_therm_threshold thrs_down_clock;
21 struct nvbios_therm_threshold thrs_critical;
22 struct nvbios_therm_threshold thrs_shutdown;
23};
24
25enum nvbios_therm_fan_type {
26 NVBIOS_THERM_FAN_UNK = 0,
27 NVBIOS_THERM_FAN_TOGGLE = 1,
28 NVBIOS_THERM_FAN_PWM = 2,
29};
30
31/* no vbios have more than 6 */
32#define NVKM_TEMP_FAN_TRIP_MAX 10
33struct nvbios_therm_trip_point {
34 int fan_duty;
35 int temp;
36 int hysteresis;
37};
38
39enum nvbios_therm_fan_mode {
40 NVBIOS_THERM_FAN_TRIP = 0,
41 NVBIOS_THERM_FAN_LINEAR = 1,
42 NVBIOS_THERM_FAN_OTHER = 2,
43};
44
45struct nvbios_therm_fan {
46 enum nvbios_therm_fan_type type;
47
48 u32 pwm_freq;
49
50 u8 min_duty;
51 u8 max_duty;
52
53 u16 bump_period;
54 u16 slow_down_period;
55
56 enum nvbios_therm_fan_mode fan_mode;
57 struct nvbios_therm_trip_point trip[NVKM_TEMP_FAN_TRIP_MAX];
58 u8 nr_fan_trip;
59 u8 linear_min_temp;
60 u8 linear_max_temp;
61};
62
63enum nvbios_therm_domain {
64 NVBIOS_THERM_DOMAIN_CORE,
65 NVBIOS_THERM_DOMAIN_AMBIENT,
66};
67
68int
69nvbios_therm_sensor_parse(struct nvkm_bios *, enum nvbios_therm_domain,
70 struct nvbios_therm_sensor *);
71
72int
73nvbios_therm_fan_parse(struct nvkm_bios *, struct nvbios_therm_fan *);
74#endif
